{"lemma":"وِزْرُ","slug":"وِزْرُ","root":"#.ز.ر","root_slug":"_-ز-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ز-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"وِزْر","root":"وزر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":12},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n41900","n41904","n41905"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%88%D9%90%D8%B2%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"burden"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"crime, sin, fault"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"arms or armour carried on the body"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/wizr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n41900","headword_ar":"وَزَرَ","root":"wzr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Mgh, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaziru","text_ar":"يَزِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wizorN","text_ar":"وِزْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bore,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carried,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a heavy load, or burden. (A, Mgh, K.) It is said in the Kur, [vi. 164, &c.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA taziru waAzirapN wizora A^uxoraY","text_ar":"وَلَا تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٌ وِزْرَ اُخْرَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Nor shall any"},{"kind":"text","text":"[soul]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bearing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a heavy burden]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bear the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heavy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burden of another"},{"kind":"text","text":"soul; (S;) i. e., its burden of sin: (Mgh, Msb:) meaning, that no one shall be punished for the sin of another;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor shall any sinning"},{"kind":"text","text":"soul"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bear the heavy burden of another"},{"kind":"text","text":"soul; every one shall be requited for his [own] deeds: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor shall any sinning"},{"kind":"text","text":"[soul]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sin by the sin of another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Akh, S, TA.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (Akh, S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazara","text_ar":"وَزَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Akh, S, A, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaziru","text_ar":"يَزِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazira","text_ar":"وَزِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawozaru","text_ar":"يَوْزَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Akh, S, A, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuzira","text_ar":"وُزِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the same and A,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuwzaru","text_ar":"يُوزَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Akh, S, K;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wizorN","text_ar":"وِزْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazorN","text_ar":"وَزْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zirapN","text_ar":"زِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wizorapN","text_ar":"وِزْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to Zj, as I have seen it [says IM] pointed and well written; (L;) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sinned:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Akh, S, A, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he bore"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a burden of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sin-"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) See also 8. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuzira","text_ar":"وُزِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was charged with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accused of, a sin."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazara liloA^amiyri","text_ar":"وَزَرَ لِلْاَمِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilos~uloTaAni","text_ar":"لِلْسُّلْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, [this I believe to be the right reading; but in the only copy of the Msb, that I have, I find it written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlslTAn","text_ar":"السلطان"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaziru","text_ar":"يَزِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, Msb;) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wazaArapN","text_ar":"وَزَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liloA^amiyri","text_ar":"لِلْاَمِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"twz~r","text_ar":"توزّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S.) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lalomaliki","text_ar":"لَلْمَلِكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAzrhu","text_ar":"وَازرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waziyr","text_ar":"وَزِير"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vicegerent"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, A, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the governor,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sultán,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"king."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2939}],"source_refs":["A","Mgh","K","Msb","TA","Akh","S"]},{"entry_id":"n41904","headword_ar":"وِزْرٌ","root":"wzr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A heavy load"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bundle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"great bundle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is carried on the back:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a weight;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vql","text_ar":"ثقل"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, [in which the syn. is written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"viqol","text_ar":"ثِقْل"},{"kind":"text","text":": so in two copies; and so app. accord. to A 'Obeyd, who makes its pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^avoqaAl","text_ar":"اَثْقَال"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and Msb [in which, in my copy, the syn. is written without syll. signs:] and K [in which it is written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"viqal","text_ar":"ثِقَل"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awozaArN","text_ar":"اَوْزَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, K.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A weapon; an instrument of war:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weapons; arms:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"silaAHN","text_ar":"سِلَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Mgh, Msb, K:) because heavy upon the wearer: (Mgh, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awozaArN","text_ar":"اَوْزَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burdens and instruments"},{"kind":"text","text":"of war, &c.; and the sing. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wizorN","text_ar":"وِزْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A 'Obeyd, TA;) or it has no sing., accord. to some. (TA.) A poet says, (S,) namely El-Aashà, (Mgh, TA.)"},{"kind":"quote","text":"waA^aEodadotu liloHarobi A^awozaArahaA\n                      \n                     \n                        rimaAHFA TiwaAlFA waxayolFA *ukuwraA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And I prepared for the war its weapons and other apparatus; long lances and male horses"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, Mgh, TA.) And it is said in the Kur, [xlvii. 5,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hay~aY taDaEa A@loHarobu A^awozaArahaA","text_ar":"حَيَّى تَضَعَ ا@لْحَرْبُ اَوْزَارَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Until the war terminates:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) because then the people thereof lay down their arms: (Mgh:) properly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until the people of the war lay down their burdens:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their weapons and burdens:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their sins."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Bd, ubi supra, and Msb, K:) and [especially]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"polytheism:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Bd, TA:) pl. as above. (Bd, Msb, &c.) This is the sense in which it is most frequently used in the traditions. (IAth.)"}],"source_refs":["A","Mgh","K","S","Msb","Fr","Bd","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n41905","headword_ar":"وَزَرٌ","root":"wzr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is the primary signification: (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mountain difficult of access,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TK:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mountain to which one betakes himself for refuge:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is the primary signification. (Aboo-Is-hák.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of refuge:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any such place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Aboo-Is-hák, K.) So in the Kur, lxxv. 11. (TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waziyrN","text_ar":"وَزِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K","TK","Msb"]}]}}